topknot
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:  1
Definition:the kempy wool growing on a sheep's head that may cause wool-blindness.


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: top knot, top-knot
